'''Tsurugi Shrine''' (劔神社) is a [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] located in [[:en:Hōfu|Hōfu]], [[:en:Yamaguchi Prefecture|Yamaguchi Prefecture]], Japan. It is a {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|2=ja|3=式内社|qq=draft|1=Shikinaisha|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikinaisha|13=User:Immanuelle|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|lt=Shikinaisha}} and was formerly Ranked as a {{ill|Gōsha (shrine)|ja|郷社|lt=Ken-sha|1=Modern_system_of_ranked_Shinto_shrines#District_shrine|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gōsha (shrine)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度}} under the old shrine Ranking system.
